2. cs.HC - The study focuses on predicting workers' safety behaviour, which is related to human-computer interaction and ergonomics. 
3. cs.CY - The paper discusses the practical implications of the developed model, which can help identify vulnerable workers and improve safety management on construction sites, indicating a focus on cybersecurity. 
4. cs.CR - The study deals with predicting and reducing occupational accidents, which is related to computer security and privacy. 
5. cs.LG - The paper employs machine learning techniques to estimate the personality-safety behaviour relationship, indicating a focus on machine learning.
